symptoms.en: For fatigue, improving appetite, relieving anxiety. Efficacious in anemia.
It reduces temperature.
Baby tonic improves the general health of children, treats flatulence, colic, dyspepsia, vomiting and deficiency of calcium. It is especially recommended during the teething period.
To restore energy and for regaining youth. Its constant use removes impotency, loss of sexual desire, quick discharge, nightfalls.
To restore energy and for regaining youth. Its constant use removes impotency, loss of sexual desire, quick discharge, nightfalls.
Specific remedy for leucoderma. For defective blood pigmentation and dermatosis. use with BARSAL drops.
For baldness and premature hair fall. It also reduces mental fatigue.
For the local application in skin diseases such as eczema, scabies, ringworm, itch, eruptions, psoriasis, scars, etc.
For urinary tract infections. It aids the passage of urinary stones. It reduces inflammation of kidney and bladder.
For all tumors
For irregularities of heart. It calms the heart and renders its movement rhythmical.
It relieves spasms and pain in gall stones and kidney stones. It also relieves neuropathic pain including sciatica and migraine.
For acute and chronic catarrh of the ear passages. For nasal catarrh & sinusitis
For the treatment of diabetes mellitus. It acts promptly in reducing the quantity of urine and diminishing the excretion of sugar in urine.
For acute & chronic diarrhea from any cause, watery stools with undigested food, loose diarrhea.
For relieving the labor pains, favouring the mother’s health and assisting in the development of child, if taken during the entire time of pregnancy. May also prevent miscarriage.
For bedwetting, bladder weakness and urinary incontinence.
For epilepsy, irritation of nerves, convulsive cramps. It lessens the frequency and intensity of fits.
It works as a diuretic. Effectively reduces oedema and ascites.
Acute and chronic conjunctivitis, blepharitis, ulcers of cornea,  glaucoma, iritis, myopia and cataract.
For allergy, sickness, lack of vital power, atrophy, cataract, tumors, old age complaints.
For fistula, exudative diathesis, ulcers. An antisupporative.
For bronchitis, laryngitis, whooping cough, chronic bronchitis and asthma.
Gastic hyperacidity, heartburn, acute and chronic gastritis, dyspepsia, chronic relapsing gastritis with or without ulceration.
For diseases of nervous origin, cervical syndrome, cervical migraine, osteochondrosis of the cervical region of vertebral column, neuralgia, state of fear, paralysis.
For nocturnal emissions, spermatorrhoea, involuntary escape of semen, discharge of prostatic fluid from slight cause.
For influenza, pain in the limbs, prostration, dull headaches, restlessness and feverish catarrh of the upper air passages.
Headaches of any origin, constitutional headaches, migraine, headaches in fever and inflammatory conditions.
For hemorrhoidal discomforts and rectal soreness.
It is helpful in relieving symptoms related to liver, gall bladder and gastrointestinal tract. It improves jaundice, lack of appetite, bitter taste in mouth, constipation and flatulence.
For hernia; specially reducible inguinal hernia and hernia of infants and children.
For intestinal diseases such as spasm, flatulence, chronic appendicitis, faecal incontinence, constipation and haemorrhoids.
For amenorrhoea, dysmenorrhoea, suppressed or late menses from nervous debility or chlorosis.
For sexual weakness in men, spermatorrhoea, general debility after sexual excess, lack of virility & weakness, impotence & lack of libido.
For pulmonary weakness, tuberculosis and bronchial asthma.
Inflammation of kidneys and bladder, renal calculi, sharp stinging pain in lumber or sacral region, crystalluria. It dissolves gravel and calculi (esp. of uric acid).
For lactating mothers. It increases the quality and quantity of milk in nursing women.
All forms of leucorrhoea during puberty, pregnancy and in climacteric.
Disturbances of menstruation, irregular menses, amenorrhoea, dysmenorrhoea, dull pains across the small of back.
For inflammation of female genital organs and regulating gynecological functions.
For mouth ulcers, soreness, inflammation of gums and boils.
For fatigue, depression, anxiety, nervous breakdown and sleeplessness.
It is effective for anal fissure, anal prolapse, internal and external piles along with associated symptoms including stinging pains, itching and bleeding.
For piles, anal fissures, itching and eczema.
For pleurisy, inter-coastal neuralgia, cough and pleuritic chest pain.
For hypertension.
For fungal infection of skin, eczema, pityriasis, ringworm, alopecia areata.
For prolapse and displacement of uterus.
For whooping cough and various types of dry cough.
For rheumatism, gout and arthritis. It is also beneficial in sciatica.
For primary chronic polyarthritis, spondyloarthritis, muscular rheumatism, uric acid diathesis, arterial and venous congestion in joints.
For acute and chronic myalgia, lumbago, after-effects of drenching, strains, overstraining, chronic rheumatism with deformations. Also a complimentary medicine for sciatica.
For injuries, falls, blows, contusions, wounds caused by sharp objects, fractures, sprains.
It helps to overcome narcotic and opium addiction.
Sciatica as a result of prolapse of intervertebral discs, spinal arthritis, paraesthesia and formication in legs.
For menstural disturbances and associated pain.
For acute and chronic catarrh of the nose and maxillary sinus. Sinusitis, polypous in children.
For all types of skin diseases.
It is a mild sleep inducing agent. It can be used for nervous excitement, insomnia, restlessness, worry and nervous palpitations.
For the auto-traumatism of masturbation, emissions and spermatorrhoea, in debiliated states of sexual organs, ready emissions and impoverished semen.
Removes sterility. Lessens the possibility of repeated miscarriage.
For disturbances of digestion with accumulation of gas, flatulent dyspepsia, heaviness, acidity and indigestion.
It shrinks goiter caused by underactive thyroid gland. Also reduces weight and arteriosclerosis. Strumeel is beneficial in conditions where iodine is indicated.
For lymphatic diathesis, tonsillar hypertrophy, chronic tonsillitis.
For acute and chronic tonsillitis, sore throat and tonsillar hypertrophy.
For quick relief of stiff & swollen joints, backaches, strains & sprains, injuries, swellings, neuralgic pains.
For gastric and duodenal ulcers, acidity, pancreatitis.
For chronic gonorrhoea and dysuria. It heals urethral inflammation.
For urinary tract infections, kidney & bladder inflammation, dysuria.
For gastroenteritis, diarrhea, dysentery, anal prolapse, glaucoma.
It is a reliable vermifuge. It can be used for worms of all types.
Vertigo of any origin, kinetosis, genetic concussions.
For nausea and vomiting, including nausea and vomiting caused by pregnancy.
For defects & weakness of male sexual organ.
It can be used for sexual asthenia, general debility in men, impotence and lack of libido. It strengthens the genital region.
